<h3>A todo list to minimize the time you spend on boring tasks

<p>
    Organize yourself and get through your work. When you leave only the time
    you need for sad tasks and starts happy tasks as soon as possible, you
    spend less time on sad tasks, maximizing the time available for happy taks.
    Thus, maximizing happyness!

<p>
    Happy Scheduler is a WebApp that allows you manage your ToDo list, that
    suggest you a starting date for your tasks. Use it to add tasks to your
    list, to show and to remove tasks from that list. You can classify if itâ€™s a
    happy or sad task. Then it schedules the tasks for you. Automagically!

